  f   o   r   (   m       i   n       e   )   e   .   h   a   s   O   w   n   P   r   o   p   e   r   t   y   (   m   )   &amp;&amp;k   .   p   u   s   h   (   m   +   "   =   "   +   e   [   m   ]   )   ;   e   =   k   .   j   o   i   n   (   l   )   ;   f   +   =   g   +   e   }   c   .   p   u   s   h   (   f   )   }   r   e   t   u   r   n       c   .   j   o   i   n   (   b   .   r   e   s   o   u   r   c   e   S   e   p   )   }   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n       r   (   a   )   {   v   a   r       b   =   a   [   h   ]   =   a   [   h   ]   |   |   {   }   ;    a   }   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n       p   (   )   {   g   &amp;&amp;g   .   i   s   S   t   u   b   &amp;&amp;g   .   r   e   p   l   a   y   (   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   (   a   ,   b   ,   c   )   {   a   =   a   [   0   ]   ;   b   =   a   [   h   ]   =   a   [   h   ]   |   |   {   }   ;   b   [   f   ]   =   b   [   f   ]   |   |   c   ;   r   (   a   )   }   )   ;   c   .   u   e   .   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   =   r   ;   g   =   n   u   l   l   }   i   f   (   !   (   1   c   .   u   e   i   n   i   t   )   )   {   v   a   r       h   =   "   m   e   t   a   d   a   t   a   "   ,   w   =   "   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   T   y   p   e   "   ,   u   =   "   f   o   r   e   s   t   e   r   C   h   a   n   n   e   l   "   ,   v   =   "   p   r   o   g   r   a   m   G   r   o   u   p   "   ,   s   =   "   m   a   r   k   e   t   p   l   a   c   e   I   d   "   ,   t   =   "   s   e   s   s   i   o   n   "   ,   f   =   "   r   e   q   u   e   s   t   I   d   "   ,   n   =   "   n   a   v   i   g   a   t   o   r   "   ,   y   =   c   .   u   e   _   b   l   i   ,   k   =   d   [   n   ]   &amp;&amp;d   [   n   ]   .   s   e   n   d   B   e   a   c   o   n   ,   q   =   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   (   a   ,   b   ,   c   ,   d   )   {   r   e   t   u   r   n   {   e   n   c   o   d   e   :   d   ,   r   e   s   o   u   r   c   e   S   e   p   :   a   ,   m   e   t   a   S   e   p   :   b   ,   m   e   t   a   P   a   i   r   S   e   p   :   c   }   }   ,   x   =   q   (   "   "   ,   "   ?    A   )   }   )   ,   A   =   q   (   "   ,   "   ,   "   @   "   ,   "   |   "   ,   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   (   a   )   {   r   e   t   u   r   n       a   .   i   d   }   )   ,   g   =   c   .   u   e   .   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   ;   y   &amp;&amp;u   e   .   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   (   {   p   r   o   g   r   a   m   G   r   o   u   p   :   "   c   s   m   "   ,   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   T   y   p   e   :   "   a   c   t   i   o   n   "   ,   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   D   a   t   a   :   [   {   f   e   a   t   u   r   e   N   a   m   e   :   "   c   s   m   -   f   e   a   t   u   r   e   s   "   ,   r   e   s   o   u   r   c   e   s   :   [   {   i   d   :   "   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   -   t   r   a   c   k   i   n   g   "   }   ]   }   ]   ,   m   e   t   a   d   a   t   a   :   {   c   s   m   :   1   }   ,   f   o   r   e   s   t   e   r   C   h   a   n   n   e   l   :   "   a   c   t   i   o   n   -   i   m   p   r   e   s   s   i   o   n   s   "   }   )   ;   k   ?   p   (   )   :   (   u   e   .   a   t   t   a   c   h   (   "   l   o   a   d   "   ,   p   )   ,   u   e   .   a   t   t   a   c   h   (   "   b   e   f   o   r   e   u   n   l   o   a   d   "   ,   p   )   )   ;   d   .    /   s   c   r   i   p   t   &gt;
